{"tid":141214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗唔係反老任，反到去日本領事館既咩","createTime":"2017-03-02T17:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T05:38:15.000Z","uid":29784,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc515f1e879865feb6a9e0db6e144a4bb41bfe5","tid":141214,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXH8Sji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXH8Sji.jpg&h=634ab640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04339504340a209d92e962301624db9a0d7f327c","tid":141214,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:34:11.000Z","msg":"皇天撃殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a543458d5be7d7cace023456570fb490baa0a1c","tid":141214,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:36:47.000Z","msg":"要玩switch ，不了"},{"pid":"e328dc14b5203ae6ee8a04ec644c8bcfa86e73d4","tid":141214,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T18:45:37.000Z","msg":"呢部機伏野居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431c09cf57bf403f60002467d2a0777e235ac5f8","tid":141214,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T20:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22df3ed8a9c0fe398f84305a2f90784e958e1737","tid":141214,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T21:27:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fecb189dae31f23c2011125927f906add6db7672","tid":141214,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T21:53:28.000Z","msg":"任天堂最近將「寵物小精靈」系列更名為「精靈寶可夢」，比卡超更被硬改成「皮卡丘」。毒撚媒體、熱血公民及熱血時報今日（5月30日）發起遊行，由遮打花園遊行到日本駐港總領事館，希望日本政府向任天堂施壓，保留港台兩地各自的「寵物小精靈」譯名，推出真正「在地化」的中文版遊戲。 發起遊行的毒撚媒體副編輯阿昇批評，今次更改譯名未有徵詢香港人的意見，而舊有譯名已沿用20年，認為今次變動踐踏香港人的文化，是香港及日本文化交流上的嚴重議題，希望日本的領事可以正視事件，尊重粵語，期望其他日本企業不要做出相同行為。 有參與遊行的熱血公民首領黃洋達表示，對於有人指今次統一譯名，只是遊戲公司的商業決定，不應到日本領事館抗議，他認為處身於現今的香港，港人面對種種的文化清洗，捍衛香港本土及粵語文化，已經成為這一代人不可逃避的責任，而事實上，對於年青的香港人而言，「寵物小精靈」是他們這一代人的記憶，就自然會對統一譯名事件敏感。 作為熱血公民及推動香港本土文化的人，黃洋達重申任何會摧殘本土文化的環節，都有責任及義務企出來說給全世界聽，即使只是一個遊戲或產品，每當牽涉本土文化，就會是一個政治事件。故此，今次遊行選擇到日本總領事館抗議，將事件提升到國際層面。 黃洋達續指，其實不少玩家已經去信任天堂公司，但有關訴求卻被無視，故熱血公民決定將訴求帶到日本領事館，並以嚴肅態度看待，同時亦希望日本方面可以嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-30-2016/30764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F05-30-2016%2F30764&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fb51784e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/05-30-2016/30764</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2017"},{"pid":"a5846ded19f0ab1fa25b703384573036f0ea1ff4","tid":141214,"uid":14862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T21:55:05.000Z","msg":"口裡說不 身體卻很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5134679741760e1ea1498f2b07f3d732dbc34a1b","tid":141214,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T22:10:26.000Z","msg":"又食熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0589d9f768ba784ccde4f70f020026ef418a27","tid":141214,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T23:17:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"264777fbee1042a559372e050146709c21236e33","tid":141214,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99df2f48461f2421c8193140b584ac7d99b0ed2c","tid":141214,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T05:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/